---
title: Portabello Mushroom & Veggie Lasagne with Bechamel Sauce & Parmesan
description: Lasagnas are a much-loved dinnertime staple and with a stack of shrooms’, veggies and a delightfully creamy bechamel sauce it will
become unbeatable. The sharp Parmesan topping brings an extra zap of flavour and you’ll adore how the cheese pulls away in strings
when you slice up and serve this gorgeous dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

